  "text": "Dietary saponins were often suspected of having a role in causing ruminant bloat [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ), but clear experimental proof for this is lacking in the literature. The absence of any positive effect in experiments where Yucca saponins were fed to ruminants (for example, [CITATION_3] might have been because animals with adapted rumen microbial population were used.",
